token_info.name: EYES OF PANDORA #1
token_info.description: EYES OF PANDORA #1 is my first Pandora's box. I engraved the panels with 6 different eyes to protect the tresure inside. Inside the box there is one of the moost precious things for me: a song i wrote for my love, you will be able to read it only if you download the OBJKT and watch inside the box. Always remind to protect the precious things, always remind that Love is the most precious one.
